Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/display: Find first CRTC and its line time in dce110_fill_display_configs
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 669f73a26f6112eedbadac53a2f2707ac6d0b9c8
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc3
Alt-commit: 4ab09785f8d5d03df052827af073d5c508ff5f63
References: stable-fixes

dce110_fill_display_configs is shared between DCE 6-11, and
finding the first CRTC and its line time is relevant to DCE 6 too.
Move the code to find it from DCE 11 specific code.

